      "data": {
        "title": "Project Summary",
        "markdown": "# 🚀 AI-Powered Recruitment Pipeline\n\n## Architecture\n- **Backend**: Node.js + Express + SQLite + GraphQL (Apollo)\n- **Frontend**: React + TypeScript + Vite + TailwindCSS\n- **AI Engine**: Gemini Pro for resume evaluation\n- **Real-time**: Socket.IO for live updates\n- **Workspace**: Jetro canvas for visual analytics\n\n## Key Features\n- PDF resume parsing & AI-powered evaluation\n- Multi-dimensional scoring (Skill, Experience, Culture, Risk)\n- Real-time WebSocket notifications\n- GraphQL API for flexible queries\n- Role-based auth with JWT\n- Audit logging\n\n## Data Pipeline\n`Resume Upload → Text Extraction → AI Scoring → Ranking → Dashboard`",
